<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7a55ac4e-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s6302"><num value="6302">§ 6302.</num><heading> Purposes</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The purposes of this chapter are—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id7a55ac4f-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s6302/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> to improve and expand the system of safety precautions that protects the welfare of professional boxers; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id7a55ac50-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s6302/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> to assist State boxing commissions to provide proper oversight for the professional boxing industry in the United States.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="id7a55ac51-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/pl/104/272/s3">Pub. L. 104–272, § 3</ref>, <date date="1996-10-09">Oct. 9, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/3310">110 Stat. 3310</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id7a55ac52-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="id7a55ac53-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="id7a55ac54-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1997-01-01">Jan. 1, 1997</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/104/272/s23">section 23 of Pub. L. 104–272</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t15/s6301">section 6301 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
